main event: A possible satellite (Echo II) was reported sighted over Nauvoo, Illinois on June 23, 1967.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 7 minutes,The object was seen by a civilian observer who described being in a tent during the sighting,The object was moving silently at a high rate of speed,The reported conclusion was that it was a probable satellite, no photographic evidence of the sighting was included.
witness description: a 13-year-old male who was outdoors in a tent
